Celebrities and influencers gathered this week to have a go at television star, Khanyi Mbau. The Comedy Central Roast was recorded live at the Teatro at Montecasino in Johannesburg. eNCA’s Theodor Mashele was there and brings us some highlights. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Celebrities and influencers gathered to have a go at television star Khanyi Mbau. The Comedy Central Roast was recorded live at the Teatro at Montecasino in Johannesburg. READ: Biden, Trevor Noah headline White House journalists' gala dinner It was the fifth South African celebrity roast and the first of a female target. The panel of roasters included veteran actor Sello Maake Ka Ncube, comedian John Vlismas and the larger-than-life Sol Phenduka. eNCA's Theodor Mashele shares more details in the video above.